title: To The Last Man ( 1933)  Action,  Romance,  Western

sources.title: To The Last Man ( 1933)  Action,  Romance,  Western
sources.description: In Kentucky just after the Civil War, the Hayden-Colby feud leads to Jed Colby being sent to prison for 15 years for murder. The Haydens head for Nevada and when Colby gets out of prison he heads there also seeking revenge.
